
1- In order to be able to use the benchmarks, you need to set the environment
variables defined in the file "setenv.sh" and source it.

2- Please change the execution options in the file "user.def"

3- Use the Makefile located in the root of the package to compile, run and plot
the curves and charts with gnuplot. 
The version 4.2 of gnuplot or later is required as it supports the charts.

4- A single compilation or execution is possible via the Makefiles situated
under the directories "src/caf" and "src/mpi".

5- Under the directory "doc", you can find a report describing the algorithms 
and the results we obtained using our ressources.
